  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Shape Sweeper</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ever wondered what happens when you give vacuum cleaners a taste for geometric shapes? Welcome to Shape Sweeper, the oddly satisfying idler where your robotic vacuum friends have developed an appetite for circles, squares, and triangles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3343570/extras/eebfd165bdebcea45cac6fe3e9c23be4.poster.avif?t=1747984401\" width=632 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3343570/extras/eebfd165bdebcea45cac6fe3e9c23be4.webm?t=1747984401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3343570/extras/eebfd165bdebcea45cac6fe3e9c23be4.mp4?t=1747984401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deploy an army of shape-hungry vacuum cleaners(PolyBots)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Merge your PolyBots to create super-powered collectors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up and create super PolyBots</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Huge tech tree with over (50+ upgrades) </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>No PolyBots were harmed in the making of this game. They're just really, really into geometry.</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💫 Regular updates and additions planned! 💫</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Shape Sweeper</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ever wondered what happens when you give vacuum cleaners a taste for geometric shapes? Welcome to Shape Sweeper, the oddly satisfying idler where your robotic vacuum friends have developed an appetite for circles, squares, and triangles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3343570/extras/eebfd165bdebcea45cac6fe3e9c23be4.poster.avif?t=1747984401\" width=632 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3343570/extras/eebfd165bdebcea45cac6fe3e9c23be4.webm?t=1747984401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3343570/extras/eebfd165bdebcea45cac6fe3e9c23be4.mp4?t=1747984401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deploy an army of shape-hungry vacuum cleaners(PolyBots)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Merge your PolyBots to create super-powered collectors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up and create super PolyBots</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Huge tech tree with over (50+ upgrades) </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>No PolyBots were harmed in the making of this game. They're just really, really into geometry.</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💫 Regular updates and additions planned! 💫</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
